Package: stancer
Title: Stance Analysis using Ensemble of LLM Agents Through `ellmer`
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Andrej", "Pawluczenko", , "a.pawluczenko@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for stance analysis using an ensemble of large language
    models. The package follows a multi-stage process in which different
    agents perform linguistic analysis, role-play as domain experts, and
    engage in structured debates to reach a final judgment. It works with
    'ellmer' chat objects, so a user can choose which models and providers
    to use. Each result includes the full reasoning and intermediate steps
    from the agents.
